       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. INVENTORY-UPDATE.

       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-ITEM-ID            PIC X(10).
       01  WS-QUANTITY           PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-NEW-QUANTITY       PIC 9(4) VALUE 0.

       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       MAIN-LOGIC.
           ACCEPT WS-ITEM-ID
           ACCEPT WS-QUANTITY
           PERFORM CALCULATE-STOCK
           PERFORM WRITE-RESULT
           STOP RUN.

       CALCULATE-STOCK.
           ADD 10 TO WS-QUANTITY GIVING WS-NEW-QUANTITY.

       WRITE-RESULT.
           DISPLAY WS-ITEM-ID WS-NEW-QUANTITY.
